cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.NI, cs.GR, cs.HC

The paper focuses on VR streaming and QoE metrics, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV). It also mentions the use of IoT and cloud computing, which falls under networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). The evaluation of the proposed method involves user studies, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper proposes a tiling scheme for VR streaming, which is related to graphics (cs.GR).
